The paper discusses problems with utility functions in agents, which is a common topic in artificial intelligence (AI) research. Therefore, cs.AI is the most likely sub-category. The paper also discusses learning models of the environment, which is a common topic in machine learning (ML) research, making cs.LG another likely sub-category. The paper also discusses self-modifying agents, which is a common topic in robotics (RO) research. Additionally, the paper discusses issues related to security and trust in agents, which are common topics in computer security (CR) and control systems (SY) research.
